 Press has reissued this harrowing and haunting novel. The Ungodly is an unforgettable story of terrible hardship and awesome courage—a story that increases our understanding of what kind of people made this nation and what a full and immeasurable price they paid.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 7aHISTORY / Expeditions & Discoveries.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150362656040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503626560423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503626560/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles